<h3 id="Gaussian-Mixture-Model"><a href="#Gaussian-Mixture-Model" class="headerlink" title="Gaussian Mixture Model"></a>Gaussian Mixture Model</h3><p>The Gaussian mixture can be interpreted in terms of discrete latent variables.</p>
<p>\begin{equation}<br>\begin{aligned}<br>    p(\textbf{x}) &#x3D; \sum_{k&#x3D;1}^{K} \pi_{k} \mathcal{N}(\textbf{x} | \mu_{k}, \Sigma_{k})<br>\end{aligned}<br>\end{equation}</p>
