<h3 id="Command"><a href="#Command" class="headerlink" title="Command"></a>Command</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># compile</span></span><br><span class="line">nvcc example.cu -o example</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># or</span></span><br><span class="line">nvcc -o example example.cu</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># run </span></span><br><span class="line">./example</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># show GPU activity</span></span><br><span class="line">nvprof ./example</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>(Slurm Commands)</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">module load gcc</span><br><span class="line">module load cuda</span><br><span class="line">srun --mem=1G --time=00:10:00 --gres=gpu nvcc example.cu -o example</span><br><span class="line">srun --mem=10G --time=00:10:00 --gres=gpu ./example</span><br><span class="line">srun --mem=10G --time=00:10:00 --gres=gpu nvprof ./example</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
